{"lemma":"غَرَضَيْ","slug":"غَرَضَيْ","root":"غ.ر.ض","root_slug":"غ-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31676","n31677","n31682","n31684","n31685"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be vexed, to be distressed"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to yearn, to long"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَرِضَ (ḡariḍa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"object of will, intention, target, desire, interest","examples":[{"text":"اَلْمُعَدَّاتُ الْمُتَوَقِّفَةُ تَصْدَأُ بَدَلَ أَنْ تَخْدِمَ أَيَّ غَرَضٍ.","english":"The idled equipment only gathers rust rather than serving any purpose."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"vexed, distressed"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31676","headword_ar":"غَرِضَ","root":"grD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDN","text_ar":"غَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was vexed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquieted by grief, and by distress of mind; he was grieved, and distressed in mind: he was disgusted; he turned away with disgust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariDa minohu","text_ar":"غَرِضَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was vexed by,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, and disquieted by grief, and by distress of mind; he was grieved, and distressed in mind, by him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"grD","text_ar":"غرض"},{"kind":"text","text":", and TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was disgusted with it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at it; he turned away from it with disgust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he feared him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K, TK: but the first and second mention only the inf. n. of the verb in this last sense.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariDa biAlmuqaAmi","text_ar":"غَرِضَ بِالمُقَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was vexed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by continuance, stay, residence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a place:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was disgusted with it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at it."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA","text_ar":"اـِذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAtahu AlgaraDu fat~ahu AlgaraDu","text_ar":"فَاتَهُ الغَرَضُ فَتَّهُ الغَرَضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ajaru","text_ar":"الضَّجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the object of aim,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavour, escapes him, so that he cannot attain it, vexation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquietude by grief, and by distress of mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disgust, crushes him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (A,) aor. as above, (K,) and so the inf. n., (A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He yearned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he yearned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longed, vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY liqaAy^ihi","text_ar":"اـِلَى لِقَايِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for meeting with him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the verb in this sense being made trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlY","text_ar":"الى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it imports the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otaAqa","text_ar":"اِشْتَاقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Han~a","text_ar":"حَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which are made trans. by the same means]: (A, TA:) [for] accord. to Akh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariDotu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"غَرِضْتُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariDotu mino","text_ar":"غَرِضْتُ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`w^ulA='i A_ilayohi","text_ar":"هٰوُلا=ءِ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I turned with vexation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disgust, from these, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; because the Arabs connect the verb [with its objective complement] by means of all these particles [mentioned above; namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlY","text_ar":"الى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) Mbr reckons"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDN","text_ar":"غَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as meaning both “ being disgusted ” and “ yearning ” or “ longing, ” among words having contrary significations; and so does Ibn-Es-Seed; (MF;) and in like manner, IKtt. (TA.) [Perhaps these derive the latter meaning from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDN","text_ar":"غَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a butt, ” or “ an object of aim, ” &c.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa Eanohu","text_ar":"غَرَضَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [in the TK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDahu","text_ar":"غَرَضَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-'Abbád, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refrained, forbore, abstained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desisted, from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it; left, relinquished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forsook, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, * K, * TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garuDa","text_ar":"غَرُضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraDN","text_ar":"غِرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was fresh, juicy, moist, not flaccid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"غَرَضَ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~Dhu","text_ar":"غرّضهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagoriyDN","text_ar":"تَغْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He plucked the thing while it was fresh, juicy, moist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not flaccid:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in some copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*~ahu","text_ar":"جَذَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistake, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"while it was so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did the thing hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurriedly, before its time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEojalahu Eano waqotihi","text_ar":"اَعْجَلَهُ عَنْ وَقْتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, O, TS, K. *) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa Als~axola","text_ar":"غَرَضَ السَّخْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~DhA","text_ar":"غرّضها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He weaned the lambs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kids, before their time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDato siqaA='ahaA","text_ar":"غَرَضَتْ سِقَا=ءَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (S,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"churned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitated, the contents of her milk-skin, and when its butter had formed in little clots but had not collected together, she poured out the milk, and gave it to people to drink."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K. *) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDotu lahu gariyDFA","text_ar":"غَرَضْتُ لَهُ غَرِيضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave him to drink fresh milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDotu lilD~ayofi gariyDFA","text_ar":"غَرَضْتُ لِلضَّيْفِ غَرِيضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I fed the guests with food that had not been kept through the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the A: but in the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahumo","text_ar":"لَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraDa","text_ar":"اَغْرَضَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyDFA","text_ar":"غَرِيضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he kneaded for them fresh dough, and did not feed them with food that had been kept through the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDahu","text_ar":"غَرَضَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a vessel, (S, K,) and a skin, and a wateringtrough; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AgrDhu","text_ar":"اغرضهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped short of filling it completely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. [See also 2.]) Thus it has two contr. significations. (S, K.) A rájiz says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laqado fadaY A^aEonaAqahun~a AlmaHoDu\n                      \n                     \n                        waAld~aA^oZu Hat~aY maA lahun~a garoDu"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHD","text_ar":"محض"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dA^Z","text_ar":"داظ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the pure milk and the fatness and fulness so that there is no deficiency in their skins"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have ransomed them from being slaughtered and sold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.] ―         -b3-  Also, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without separating it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa AlbaEiyra","text_ar":"غَرَضَ البَعِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", as appears from the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoriDN","text_ar":"مَغْرِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for otherwise, by rule, it would be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoraDN","text_ar":"مَغْرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoD","text_ar":"غَرْض"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2248},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AgotirDhu","text_ar":"اغْتِرضهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bound the she-camel with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroDap","text_ar":"غُرْضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoD","text_ar":"غَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraDahaA","text_ar":"اَغْرَضَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa Albagiyra biAlgaroDi","text_ar":"غَرَضَ البَغِيرَ بِالغَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","Mgh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31677","headword_ar":"غرّض","root":"grD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagoriyDN","text_ar":"تَغْرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate fresh flesh-meat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDa","text_ar":"غَرَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gar~iDo fiY siqaAy^aka","text_ar":"غَرِّضْ فِى سِقَايَكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fill not thy skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"completely; leave a portion unfilled in thy skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN baHorN laA yugar~aDu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ بَحْرٌ لَا يُغَرَّضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a sea"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not become exhausted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~D","text_ar":"غرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafak~aha","text_ar":"تَفَكَّهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA.) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He affected jesting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for it is] said in the I. to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfukaAhapu","text_ar":"الفُكَاهَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuzaAHu","text_ar":"المُزَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31682","headword_ar":"غَرْضٌ","root":"grD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroDapN","text_ar":"غُرْضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appertenance of a camel's saddle of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HizaAm","text_ar":"حِزَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroj","text_ar":"سَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaAn","text_ar":"بِطَان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatab","text_ar":"قَتَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"girth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore girth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSodiyr","text_ar":"تَصْدِير"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HizaAm","text_ar":"حِزَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) pl. of the former,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraADN","text_ar":"اَغْرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] (S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoruDN","text_ar":"اَغْرُضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also a pl. of pauc.] (IB) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwDN","text_ar":"غُرُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of mult.]: and of the latter, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroDN","text_ar":"غُرْضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather this is a coll. gen. n.,] (S, K,) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busorN","text_ar":"بُسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busorapN","text_ar":"بُسْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruDN","text_ar":"غُرُضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) [Hence the saying of Mohammad,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroD","text_ar":"غُرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall not be bound [upon camels by pilgrims] except to three mosques; the sacred mosque [of Mekkeh], and my mosque [of ElMedeeneh], and the mosque [El-Aksà] of Beytel-Makdis [or Jerusalem]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoDN","text_ar":"غَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (accord. to some, in the verse cited in the first paragraph, S, TA) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of what thou hast left"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDiEu maA tarakotahu","text_ar":"مَوْضِعُ مَا تَرَكْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA'","text_ar":"ماء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='K","text_ar":"مَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as written in the S [and K], TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and not put into it anything:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) and is said by some to be like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amot","text_ar":"اَمْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] in a skin. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state of folding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth, K.) And A man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having folds"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwD","text_ar":"غُرُوض"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the body when he has been fat and then has become lean."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tawayotu Alv~awoba EalaY guruwDihi","text_ar":"طَوَيْتُ الثَّوْبَ عَلَى غُرُوضِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwrihi","text_ar":"غُرُورِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I folded the garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, according to its first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"original, foldings."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Ibn- 'Abbád, Z, Sgh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","IB","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31684","headword_ar":"غَرَضٌ","root":"grD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A butt, a mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of aim, at which one shoots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throws;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that thou settest up"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^amovalotahu","text_ar":"مَا اَمْثَلْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to shoot or throw at:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraADN","text_ar":"اَغْرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tat~axi*uwA $ayoy^FA fiyhi Alr~awHu garaDFA","text_ar":"لَا تَتَّخِذُوا شَيْيًا فِيهِ الرَّوحُ غَرَضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye shall not take a thing in which is the vital principle as a butt"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And hence one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsu A^agoraADu Almaniy~api","text_ar":"النَّاسُ اَغْرَاضُ المَنِيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mea are the butts of destiny,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of death"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalotaniY garaDFA li$atomika","text_ar":"جَعَلْتَنِى غَرَضًا لِشَتْمِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou madest me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hast made me, a butt for thy reviling"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object of aim"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavour"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pursuit, of desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of intention"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purpose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a scope;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any end which one endeavours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intends,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes, to attain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of desire:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"advantage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good, which one seeks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes, to attain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtain, from a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so much used in this tropical sense as to be, in this sense, conventionally regarded as proper. (MF.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDuhu ka*aA","text_ar":"غَرَضُهُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His object of aim"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavour"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pursuit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his object of want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of desire, is such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala","text_ar":"فَعَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ligaraDK SaHiyHK","text_ar":"لِغَرَضٍ صَحِيحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted, for a just,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right, object of aim"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahimotu","text_ar":"فَهِمْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaDaka","text_ar":"غَرَضَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I understood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have understood, thine object of aim"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thine intention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSodaka","text_ar":"قَصْدَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) [See another ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariDa","text_ar":"غَرِضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which it is also the inf. n.]"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","Msb","B","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31685","headword_ar":"غَرِضٌ","root":"grD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", when followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vexed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquieted by grief, and by distress of mind; grieved, and distressed in mind: disgusted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turning away with disgust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, when followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Yearning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yearning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing, vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]}]}}